# Market Scout environment.
#
# Geocoding and nearby places use FREE APIs:
# - Nominatim (OpenStreetMap) for address -> coordinates
# - Overpass (OpenStreetMap) for nearby businesses
# These are always live and need no keys.
#
# Reddit and AI synthesis are optional and will fall back to demo mode if keys
# are missing. Copy this file to ".env.local" and fill in what you have.

# --- Reddit (local discussion) [OPTIONAL] ---------------------------------
# Create a "script" app at https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps to get these.
# Leave blank to use demo data.
REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=
REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=
REDDIT_USER_AGENT=market-scout/0.1 by u/yourusername

# --- Anthropic (AI synthesis) [OPTIONAL] ----------------------------------
# Leave blank to use deterministic demo synthesis.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Optional tuning -------------------------------------------------------
# Force sample data even when keys are present (handy for demos):
# MARKET_SCOUT_FORCE_MOCK=1
# MARKET_SCOUT_RADIUS_METERS=2500
# MARKET_SCOUT_MAX_PLACES=40
# MARKET_SCOUT_MAX_REDDIT=25
# MARKET_SCOUT_AI_MODEL=claude-sonnet-5
